Music x THE @barackobama x THE Bruce @springsteen ...I AM IN⭐️ #RenegadesPodcast, is their new podcast talking all things Music, Race & Fatherhood. They clearly have unique life experiences and that’s what makes this MANDATORY LISTENING for me☀️

Last week, I was curious about President Obama’s unique global upbringing and his connection to music. I wanted to know about his musical influences...so I asked!!! 

✨AND HE ANSWERED✨

I love how music can connect us to our global community and also serve as a tool for learning. I can't wait to check out the sounds of the Congo and the beautiful meditation melodies played in Java!

node.text: So many of us know how Black Women are rarely allowed safe spaces; we already traverse the world weary of our surroundings. To think of how quickly state-sanctioned violence was able to perpetuate her home, was able to disregard her life and light, only reaffirm the need to reimagine infrastructures that give us the right to just be. #BlackLivesMatter #SayHerName
